snippet.textDisplay:
कांग्रेस सरकार ने देश की सेना और युद्ध के लिए आवश्यक सैन्य साजो-सामान पर बहुत भयानक लापरवाही बरती । 
कांग्रेस सरकार की पड़ौसियों से शान्ती रखने के लिए और पाकिस्तान-चीन को संतुष्ट रखने के लिए, दोनों को भारत की जमीन के बड़े भू-भाग के सौंपने और भारत का अधिकार त्याग देने तक का विश्वासघाती और देशद्रोही रवैया अपनाया । बिलकुल यही रवैया 2014 से पहले की तमाम बीजेपी सरकार का रहा ।

लेकिन 2014 से बीजेपी सरकार ने सेना, सैन्य साजो-सामान और सेना के लिए जरूरी आधारभूत संरचनाओ पर अच्छा काम किया और भारत की भौगोलिक अखंडता को सर्वोच्च महत्व दिया है ।

लेकिन...लेकिन...लेकिन ! 
इसी बीजेपी सरकार ने 2014 से,  चीन से आर्थिक और व्यापारिक संबन्धो में बहुत आपराधिक लापरवाही बरती, जिससे चीन ने भारत से भरपूर धन कमाया और उसकी वही आर्थिक मजबूती अब भारत पर सैन्य ताकत के जोर के रूप में भारत पर भारी पड़ गयी ।

snippet.textDisplay:
Kalaripayattu 
The oldest known martial art is an Indian martial art called kalaripayattu.
Bodhidharma
Shaolin temple established
Bodhidharma the third son of Hindu King PALLAVA  was a TAMIL prince and second student of lord Buddha (Gautama Siddhartha)-(Enlightened One) from ancient India is traditionally credited as the transmitter of Chan Buddhism to China, and regarded as its first Chinese patriarch. According to Chinese legend, Bodhidarma also began the physical training of the monks of Shaolin Monastery that led to the creation of Shaolin kung fu.
Kung Fu originated from Shaolin temple with a base taken from Kalaripayattu. Kung Fu is not a local martial art in china before the aririval of Bodhidharma from India. It is a highly skilled profession that can be taught only in Shaolin Temple ( genuine).
Chinese martial arts including Kung Fu have their roots in India. It is through Buddhism did come to China from India. 
Bodhidharma is regarded as the first patriarch of the tradition that was subsequently known as Chan in China, Zen in Japan, Sŏn in Korean, and Thien in Vietnam. Those names correspond to the pronunciation of the Sanskrit word dhyana ancient Hindu philosophy of(“meditation”) from INDIA translated in Chinese, Japanese, Korean, and Vietnamese, respectively. snippet.textDisplay:
சித்தர்களின் கருத்துக்களை ஆழ்ந்து படித்தால் பல உண்மைகள் நமக்கு புரியவரும்  

பெரியார் திமுக  வினர்  இவர்களை  விட உண்மையில்  மிக அதிகமான விமர்சனகளை  முன்  வைத்தவர்கள்  சித்தர்கள் தான்

 *எடுத்துகாட்டு* : 

நீண்ட குரங்கையும் நெடிய பருந்தையும் வேண்ட பயன் வருமோ !   
-  *குதம்பை  சித்தர்* 

வீண் பயிலும்  வேதம் எல்லாம் தேடி காணார் 
-  *திருமூலர் சித்தர்* 

கோவிலாவது  ஏதடா  குலங்களாவது  ஏதடா ? 
-   *சிவவாக்கியர்* 

உத்தரம் இப்படியே  புராணம் காட்டி 
உலகத்தில் *பாரதம்* போல் கதை உண்டாக்கி  
-  *அகத்தியர் சித்தர்* 

கல் செம்பை தெய்வம் என்று உருகுவர் பூஜிப்பர்  கிரியை  என்பர் 
-  *வால்மீகி* 

கல்லினை செம்பினை கட்டையை கும்பிட்டால் புல்லறிவாகுமடி குதம்பாய் !
                 -  *குதம்பை சித்தர்* 

தந்திரம் இல்லையடி  
சமயம் அழிந்ததடி  
                -  *அகப்பேய் சித்தர்* 

சதுர்வேதம் ஆறுவகைச் சாத்திரம்  பல 
தந்திரம் புராணங்களை   சாற்றும் ஆகமம்  
விதவிதமான வான வேறு நூல்களும் 
வீணான நூல்களே  
          - *பாம்பாட்டி  சித்தர்* 

இன்னும் பல உதாரணகள் கூறிக்கொண்டே  செல்லலாம்  *நம் வழிபாட்டு முறை தவறானது என்பது சித்தர்களின்  கருத்து* 

அப்படிஎன்றால் சித்தர்கள் கூறும் சரியான வழிபாட்டு முறையை  அறிய முற்பட  வேண்டும் 

இதை விடுத்தது  கடவுள் மறுப்பு  கொள்கை  உள்ளவரோடு  வாதம் செய்வதும் பொய் மதவாதி (அகரம்,உகரம் அறியாதவர்)கருத்துக்களை உயர்த்தி பிடிப்பது  இரண்டும் ஒன்றுதான்.

snippet.textDisplay: Universities should be exemplary institutions that groom the future citizens. You don't need to advise an institution that is supposed to impart values along with bookish knowhow, that they should not allow conflicts, hostility, hate, etc. But when the values are lost it is like what Lord Jesus would call "the salt losing its savour" Are govts run by politicians need to teach the universities what they should do? Yet, the situation had demanded it in a perverse ambiance built by certain pernicious groups. It isn't easy to do good things in a society where the voice of fissiparous tendencies are strong. There is indeed every scope for misuse of the law by the overzealous officials, but is it reason enough to avoid a legislation in the needed situation? Are we going to scrape criminal laws because they are often misused? Well, we understand that it is too much to expect sense from self serving power groups poised to oppose all good things by cunning arguments

snippet.textDisplay:
Introduction to Politician Imran Khan: हिंदुस्तान का शेखचल्ली मीडिया चला इमरान खान से रोमांस करने अभी अभी तो इसकी शिनाख्त भी नहीं हुवी के ये है कौन? इमरान खान बड़के मारेने वाला शक़्श है, इसकी करनी और कथनी में बनावटी और दिखावा होता है हे बांग्ला देश युद्ध में जिस जनरल नियाजी ने भारत को सरेंडर किया उसका सगा रिश्तेदार है, और जाहिर है के ये भी नियाजी कबीले से ही है . इसका पाकिस्तान फौज के साथ पुराना रिश्ता है. 
दूसरा, शेख रशीद जो कश्मीर में आंकवादी कैंप चलता है वह उसके पार्टीका ओहदेदार है और पाक आर्मी का पीटीआई में कण्ट्रोल और कमांड के लिए दाखिल हुवा है और दुनिया के पश्चिमी देशो में ये शेख रशीद को ब्लैक लिस्टेड है और उन मुल्को में इसकेलिए एंट्री नहीं है.
तीसरा, पंजाब में दहशदगर्द तंजी मे हाफिज सईद और तहरीकेलब्बेक रसूल्ललाह  जनाब कादरी भी पाक फौज की तरफ से इंतेखाबात में मुस्लिम लीग नवाज़ के वोट काटने के लिए उत्तरी जिससे पीटीआई को बढ़त मिले और वही हुवा. 
चौथा, इमरान हमेशा खुले आम तालिबान का समर्थन करता है और खैबर पख्तून ख्वा के सरकारी बजट से करोडो रुपये डोनेशन में ऑफिशियली देता रहा है इसलिए इसको तालिबान खान कहा जाता रहा है.
पांचवा, इसने आते ही कश्मीर राग आलापना शुरू किया जैसे कश्मीर कोई इंडिया पाकिस्तान का क्रिकेट मैच हो, अभी इसके पीछे के पाक फौज और नॉन स्टेट एक्टर्स हावी हो रहे है यह उनकी जुबान बोल रहा है.  क्युकी इमरान खान इनसे फिरकापरस्त दहशदगर्द तंजीमो से घिरा है और वह इसको ज्यादा दिन चलने नहीं देंगे ये तो सिर्फ मोहरा है.

snippet.textDisplay:
The theory that we have some herd immunity against Covid-19 is very interesting. To those who don't understand the term herd immunity, here's a quick allegory.
Suppose 60% buffaloes in a herd have ability to fight of predators like Lions and Hyena's. 
So when a Lion attacks and is repelled by a Buffalo at the periphery that has 'immunity',
even the Buffaloes at the center of the herd that don't have that immunity are protected. The more people that are immune, the more the non-immune are also protected because the immune people prevent spread of the disease.
Now, we should test for antibodies aggressively as soon as possible and determine if there is any credence to it...

snippet.textDisplay:
God sent his Son Jesus Christ to saved you from all your sins. As He said in the book of *John **3:16* - _For God so loved the world, that he gave his only begotten Son, that whosoever believe on him should not perish, but have everlasting life_

_Christ died on the cross for your sins, was buried and third day He rose from the dead_ - *1Corinthians 15:1-4 Gospel of Salvation*

What it means? It means your death has been paid! What death? *The death of sin.* _The wage of sin is death but the gift of God is eternal life through Jesus Christ our Lord_ - *Romans **6:23*

Believe him and you will be saved. It's simple. As Paul said in the book of *Ephesians 2:8-9* - _For by grace are ye saved through faith; and that not of yourselves: it is the gift of God: Not of works, lest any man should boast_

To be a good person means nothing. Why? Because we aren‘t saved by works, but by grace alone through faith alone in Christ alone.

*What should I do to become a child of God?*

*A* – Admit you are a sinner in need of a Savior. As it is written: _There is non righteous, no, not one_ – *Romans **3:10**.* _For all have sinned, and come short of the glory of God_ – *Romans **3:23*

*B* – Believe on finished redemptive work of Jesus Christ on the Cross – _Christ died for your sins, was buried and third day He rose again_ – *1Cor 15:1-4 Gospel of Salvation.* If you want to enter to the Kingdom of Heaven, you must have a faith like a child – children trust their parents. Why I mentioned parents? Because God is our Creator; He is our Father; He is our Parent - _Before I formed you in the womb I knew you, before you were born I set you apart_ – *Jeremiah 1:5*

*C* – Call on the name of the Lord and you will be saved - _If you declare with your mouth, “Jesus is Lord,” and believe in your heart that God raised him from the dead, you will be saved. For it is with your heart that you believe and are justified, and it is with your mouth that you profess your faith and are saved_ – *Romans 10:9-10.* _For everyone who calls on the name of the Lord will be saved_ – *Romans **10:13*

Jesus Christ is the shower/water that cleans us of all unrighteousness. _Come now, let us settle the matter, says the Lord. Though your sins are like scarlet, they shall be as white as snow; thought they are red as crimson, they shall be like wool_ - *Isaiah **1:18* 

Shalom, God bless you all

snippet.textDisplay:
When Article 370 was introduced, it was labelled as a temporary provision which dragged on for last 70 yrs. Constituent assembly had the power for recommending the abrogation of Article 370 to the President. 

However, in 1957 the constituent assembly was dissolved by the J&K state government so that no one can touch article 370. Farqook Abdullah had once said that even after 100 yrs also when everyone will forget Modi...than also article 370 will stay in J&K.

But Modi had planned it very diligently like Chanakya. First, BJP had an unholy alliance with PDP than later decided to withdraw support and imposed Governor's rule. Than in Dec 2018, the President of India issued a proclamation under article 356 of the constitution for implementation of the ST bill in J&K and sent it to the Superme court for approving the J&K's power of the state's legislative assembly be transferred to the authority of the Parliament so that ST bill can be implemented in J&K. And SC approved it. Now all powers of state was with the Governor.

Finally, on 5th August 2019, another amendment (367) bill was passed which gave power of the Constituent Assembly to the J&K legislative assembly. 
Since, the power of the legislative assembly was with the Governor, subsequently on the same day... a Gazette was issued by the President of India, where it had the Governor's approval (which had the vested power of the constituent assembly) for aborgation of the article 370.

And finally, on recommendation of the Parliament (both houses), the President of India was pleased to declare that, as of 6th Aug 2019, all clauses of Article 370 will cease to be operative...

That's Modi's masterstroke

For general information :
Harish Salve , in his brilliant exposition and dissection, made use of a wprd several times,  which was , " disapply " ; and it's bound to confuse many people , for most people have never encountered it , in their livea and there's a reason why.
Aa a matter of course, I'd , too advise against , ever using this word in general address.
This is a term that has specific legal implications and in commonplace writing , it's not used, hence more often than not people haven't had ever heard of it.
It means broadly, to  decline to apply a rule or law that previously applied.

snippet.textDisplay:
What India can learn from Denmark:
------------------------------------------------

In Denmark, the left and right have come together in dealing with the threat of Islamization of Denmark. Denmark has introduced over 100 legislations in the last year or so to restrict immigration of Muslims into the country in the future, restricting family reunions, and even sending back naturalized Muslims to the respective countries they came from. Denmark has also introduced measures to educate Muslim children from age one so that they're better assimilated. Burqa is banned and Muslim women are compelled to modernize themselves and work and not rely upon doles. 

Muslims constitute 5% of Denmark's population. The experience of the rest of Europe says that at this level rapid Islamization of society begins. Society is forced to be sensitive toward Islamic beliefs. Burqa and hijab become prevalent. Demands for banning alcohol are heard more frequently. Any genuine concern with the sliding back of a modern society into seventh century medieval barbarism is branded as racism and Islamophobia. Leftists propagate the myth that younger generations of Muslims integrate better with the mainstream. Data from the UK, collected over a decade, falsifies this claim. An overwhelming majority of British-born Muslims in the age group of 16-24 are more radical than their immigrant parents. They crave for the sharia. They embrace the burqa and hijab. It seems that the mere presence of a modern western society actually galvanizes the younger generation of Muslims to radicalize themselves. 

A modern society cannot accommodate Islam. Islam cannot reform itself from within. A direct confrontation is inevitable. A direct ridicule of everything Islam considers sacred is a necessity. A Muslim must understand that he cannot respond violently. The state should have an effective police force to crackdown on anyone who protests violently or disruptively. 

In the Indian context, all children should be mandated to learn classical music and dance both of which Islam forbids. Yoga should be compulsory to all Indians. Ban the burqa, hijab, beards, and skullcaps. No public namaz. All should be required to celebrate traditional Indian festivals such as Diwali and Navaratri and offer obeisance to gods and goddesses which Islam forbids. The Danes have shown the way. I hope Indians emulate them.

snippet.textDisplay:
The irony of India is that there is a party called congress ruled India for 66 years. Rahul Gandhi doesn’t have any sense of economy, foreign policy, internal security or anything which can support Rahul Gandhi as next PM.
Firstly, more than 70% of revenue through taxes are collected by a small group of large and medium business.
Secondly, a huge amount of money is spend on infrastructure and funding reservations.
Now Rahul Gandhi hates these huge tax paying businesses yet he will pitch for giving reservation to anyone who’s willing to vote congress.
Imagine if these businesses closes and move out of India what will happen. There will be huge unemployment, no money to develop infrastructure, no reservation funding, no military infrastructure and equipment.
I think honest intellectuals should research why India is the top importer of military hardware and lacking the basic infrastructure and defense firms.
If we can go by simple logic, congress never wanted defense manufacturing in India because there won’t be any cuts and bribes like they get from Augusta Westland, bofors and few other deals.
There was a lot of Indian startups which closed or their patent technology was sold to foreign firms because bribes were asked to clear defense deals.

Secondly, a huge amount of money is spend on infrastructure and funding reservations.

Imagine if these businesses closes and move out of India what will happen. There will be huge unemployment, no money to develop infrastructure, no reservation funding, no military infrastructure and equipment.
